                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        
        <br>
        <p><strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong></p>
        <p>This SaaS Agreement template should be customized for your specific service offerings, pricing, and business model. Review with legal counsel to ensure compliance with applicable laws.</p>
        
